rows.label: fev11_050_125_msg0001
rows.name:
This looks like a good spot to set
up camp.

rows.label: fev11_050_125_msg0002
rows.name:
Yeah.
I'll start preparing the food.

rows.label: fev11_050_125_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh wow, you're a star Shin. What
do you reckon you'll make?

rows.label: fev11_050_125_msg0004
rows.name:
Let's see, now... I should be able
to get my hands on a few choice
ingredients around here.

rows.label: fev11_050_125_msg0005
rows.name:
If we can find some Iiran Trout,
Deviled Onions and Sour Avocados,
I could stew them together...

rows.label: fev11_050_125_msg0007
rows.name:
It's absolutely divine! You'll join us for
a bite, won't you, Satahiko?

rows.label: fev11_050_125_msg0009
rows.name:
Perfect! Then let's set to work and
hunt for those ingredients!

rows.label: fev11_050_125_msg0010
rows.name:
All three of those things should be
easy to come by around here. No
need to travel off the beaten path.
